data.name: lblGmailInfo.Text
data.value: Note: Downloading Google email into TrulyMail (or other email client) requires two changes to your Google Mail account: 1) You must enable POP in your account https://mail.google.com/support/bin/answer.py?answer=13273 2) You must clear the 'captcha' on your account http://www.google.com/accounts/DisplayUnlockCaptcha

data.name: Label37.Text
data.value:
Using an email account is a bit more involved than using a TrulyMail account. However, this wizard will take you through it step-by-step, providing help all the way through.
Note: Your email settings are NEVER stored on the TrulyMail server, they are only on your computer. This ensures your privacy.
